revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Thing_Spawn}}
{{Special|135|tid, type, angle, newtid|Thing|Spawn}}

Spawns a thing using its [[spawn ID]]. For spawning things by name, use [[SpawnSpot]] instead.

* ''tid'': [[Thing ID]] of the map spot where to spawn the thing
* ''type'': Type of thing to spawn, from the list of [[spawn numbers]]
: When using this special on a [[linedef]] or a [[thing]] in [[UDMF]], you can use the {{c|arg1str}} property to define a class name instead of the {{c|arg1}} property to define a spawn number.
* ''angle'': [[Definitions#Byte_Angles|Byte angle]] for the thing to face
* ''newtid'': [[TID]] to give spawned thing

